thread.title_full: NORCO: Oktoberfest set for Saturday, Oct. 17 - Press Enterprise

author: AMY ZAHN
title: NORCO: Oktoberfest set for Saturday, Oct. 17
text:
By AMY ZAHN / CONTRIBUTING 16, 2015 Updated: 4:32 p.m. NORCO: Oktoberfest set for Saturday, Oct. 17 More The Norco American Legion Auxiliary will be serving up German food at Oktoberfest. PAUL RODRIGUEZ, , PAUL RODRIGUEZ, FILE PHOTO Related article Â» The Norco American Legion Auxiliary is hosting its annual Oktoberfest celebration noon to 5 p.m. today at 3888 Old Hamner Road, Norco. There will be music, raffles and German food.
Admission is free and open to the public. The event benefits local veterans and children. Information: 951-371-9108
Contact the writer: community@pe.com
